                        <TABLE style="WORD-BREAK: break-all" border=0 width=650><TBODY><TR><TD>（1）当悬线的拉力最大时，摆球通过最低点，由图读出t=0.2s时摆球正通过最低点，t=0.5s时摆球正通过最高点，则摆球的摆动周期大约T=4×（0.5-0.2）s=1.2s．由图看出，摆球经过最低点时悬线的拉力随时间在减小，说明存在空气阻力，摆球机械能不断减小．<br>（2）①通过描点法作图，如图所示：<br>②由单摆的周期公式T=<span dealflag="1"  mathtag="math" >2π<table cellspacing="-1" cellpadding="-1" style="width:auto;display:inline-table;*display:inline;vertical-align:middle;margin:0;padding:0;text-align:center;line-height:normal;"><tr><td ><div style="width:6px;background: url('http://pic2.mofangge.com/upload/papers//20140610/20140610221349897125.png') repeat-y; height: 1px;overflow: hidden" muststretch="v"></div><div style="width:6px;background: url('http://pic2.mofangge.com/upload/papers//20140610/20140610221349944184.png') no-repeat; height: 7px; overflow: hidden"></div></td><td style="padding:0;padding-left: 2px; border-top: black 1px solid;line-height:normal;padding-top:1px"><table cellspacing="-1" cellpadding="-1" style="width:auto;display:inline-table;*display:inline;vertical-align:middle;margin:0;padding:0;text-align:center;line-height:normal;" style="display:inline-table;vertical-align:middle"><tr><td style="border-bottom:1px solid black">l</td></tr><tr><td>g</td></tr></table></td></tr></table></span>，得：L=<span  mathtag="math" ><table cellspacing="-1" cellpadding="-1" style="width:auto;display:inline-table;*display:inline;vertical-align:middle;margin:0;padding:0;text-align:center;line-height:normal;" style="display:inline-table;vertical-align:middle"><tr><td style="border-bottom:1px solid black;padding-bottom:1px;font-size:90%">g<span><span>T</span><span style="vertical-align:super;font-size:90%">2</span></span></td></tr><tr><td >4<span><span>π</span><span style="vertical-align:super;font-size:90%">2</span></span></td></tr></table></span><br>所以图中的图线斜率表示<span  mathtag="math" ><table cellspacing="-1" cellpadding="-1" style="width:auto;display:inline-table;*display:inline;vertical-align:middle;margin:0;padding:0;text-align:center;line-height:normal;" style="display:inline-table;vertical-align:middle"><tr><td style="border-bottom:1px solid black">g</td></tr><tr><td >4<span><span>π</span><span style="vertical-align:super;font-size:90%">2</span></span></td></tr></table></span><br>g=4π<sup>2</sup>k=4×π<sup>2</sup>×<span  mathtag="math" ><table cellspacing="-1" cellpadding="-1" style="width:auto;display:inline-table;*display:inline;vertical-align:middle;margin:0;padding:0;text-align:center;line-height:normal;" style="display:inline-table;vertical-align:middle"><tr><td style="border-bottom:1px solid black">1</td></tr><tr><td>4</td></tr></table></span>=9.86m/s<sup>2</sup><br>③由图可知，只有第1次测量数据偏离直线较远，也说明摆长太短，测量误差较大，故选：A<br>故答案为：（1）1.2s，减小；（2）①如图b<br><img alt="" src="http://pic2.mofangge.com/upload/papers//20140610/201406102213500064038.png" ><br>②9.86m/s<sup>2</sup>③A．</TD></TR></TBODY></TABLE>
